      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">What is EOS? The Entrepreneurial Operating System Explained</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">EOS, the Entrepreneurial Operating System, gives leadership teams a simple, practical structure to clarify their vision, strengthen teamwork, and boost performance through accountability. This guide covers its six components, how to implement it, the benefits, and how AI agents and OTP support EOS practices.</p>
