      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--ink)] mt-8 mb-3">How Are AI Agents Integrated as Collaborative Team Members Within EOS Teams?</h3>
      <p>AI agents can be integrated into EOS frameworks to augment team capabilities through collaboration and efficiency. They assist in routine data analytics and provide actionable insights, freeing human team members to focus on higher-value tasks. By embracing AI's potential within EOS applications, organizations can elevate their operational efficiency and improve team dynamics significantly.</p>

